Chicken cordon bleu casserole

https://jenniferbanz.com/chicken-cordon-bleu-casserole#recipe

Dont use water
Use less butter since using chicken thighs

6 Boneless skinless chicken breast, cooked and chopped
    4g salt (0.5+ tsp salt)

80g jambon coupé en petits morceaux
    1.5g salt

50 g Butter, softened
227 g Cream cheese, softened   
    2g salt (enough salt for itself)
1 tsp Dijon mustard
    0.5g salt
1 tsp White wine vinegar

140g emmental rapé
